As you slice through the cake, your senses will be surrounded in an intoxicating aroma of rich cocoa and chocolate. The moist soft layers of chocolate cake, engulfed in the chocolate ganache, provides a heavenly base for a melody of flavors.

fields.description: Our irresistible almond Dutch truffle cake combines the rich flavor of Dutch truffle with the delightful crunch of almonds. Making a perfect blend of textures on your palette. The silky smooth ganache engulfing the cake layers with the crunchy almonds make it delectable. The rich almonds and chocolate make it a luxurious dessert. Make any occasion special with this cake.

fields.title: Walnut Dutch Truffle Cake (Eggless)
fields.tags: cakes, chocolate cakes, dutch truffle cakes, walnut cakes
fields.short_description: Satisfy Your Sweet Tooth with the Decadent Almond Dutch Truffle Cake
fields.description: For those with a sweet tooth, the walnut dutch truffle cake is a lovely treat. This cake is constructed using a thick, moist sponge cake that has been flavoured with walnuts to give it a nutty, somewhat sweet flavour. The best Dutch cocoa powder and heavy cream are used to create a layer of rich, velvety chocolate truffle that is then used to cover the cake. As a result, the cake has a creamy, silky texture that melts in your mouth. The cake's crisp texture from the walnuts contrasts beautifully with the creamy truffle. The nuts also contribute to a more nuanced flavour profile by bringing the sweetness of the truffle into harmony. If you enjoy the flavours of chocolate and nuts, this cake is the ideal treat for you. The flavour of the two together will make you feel content and joyful. Chopped walnuts are saprinkled on top of the cake to give texture and create a nice visual contrast with the rich and creamy truffle. The Walnut Dutch Truffle Cake is sure to please, whether you're searching for a sweet treat to accompany your coffee or tea or a dessert to round out a meal. Therefore, why not reward yourself with this delectable cake today and enjoy the sweet flavours of walnuts and chocolate truffle!

fields.description: Welcome to the land of chocolate. This cake is for all the chocolate lovers. The cake is simply delicious and is truly divine. The truffle is made from the finest Dutch cocoa powder and heavy cream, which creates a smooth and velvety texture that will melt in your mouth. It is one of the most decadent cakes among an array of cakes. The Dutch Truffle Devine Cake is perfect for special occasions such as birthdays, anniversaries, or holidays. It is also a great choice for those who love chocolate and want a dessert that is both indulgent and satisfying. The cake is for all those who are chocoholic!

fields.title: Sacher Torte (Eggless)
fields.short_description: Experience the ultimate chocolate indulgence with the world-renowned Sacher Torte
fields.description: In the year 1832, the Chancelor of Vienna, Prince Klemens von Metternich was in a dilemma when the gratuity to please his royal guests overcame the better of him. As fate would have it of all the bad times, this day couldn't get any worse as the Chancelor's Head Pastry Chef fell sick ! Naturally this enormous responsibilty was handed down to the Head Chef's Apprentice, a 16-year old boy called Franz Sacher, who, under all this tremendous pressure and after hearing the exact warning words from the Prince which went like, " I hope you won't disgrace me tonight " , still managed to create an impressive masterpiece of concoctions, pleasing the Prince and which would leave an everlasting impression for centuries to come. This Classic Dessert, later named after its inventor, Franz Sacher, came to be known as "Sacher-Torte" and is a sacred antique passed down from generation to generation in Vienna. But the Original Recipe is Hotel Sacher's best kept secret and protected with a trademark still. Oven Fresh's Sacher-Torte is made with two layers of spongy Chocolate Dacquoise in between which delectable Apricot Jam is spread and ultimately glazed with Belgian Chocolate Ganache making it a flavourful replica of Sacher's Invention ! Finally garnished with pure chocolate & cocoa powder, this Torte is ready to reach your doorstep in a jiffy ! fields.title: Sacher Torte With Gold Varakh 99.9% (Eggless)
fields.short_description: "Indulge in the ultimate luxury with Sacher Torte topped with pure 99.9% Gold Varakh!
fields.description: In the year 1832, the Chancelor of Vienna, Prince Klemens von Metternich was in a dilemma when the gratuity to please his royal guests overcame the better of him. As fate would have it of all the bad times, this day couldn't get any worse as the Chancelor's Head Pastry Chef fell sick ! Naturally this enormous responsibilty was handed down to the Head Chef's Apprentice, a 16-year old boy called Franz Sacher, who, under all this tremendous pressure and after hearing the exact warning words from the Prince which went like, " I hope you won't disgrace me tonight " , still managed to create an impressive masterpiece of concoctions, pleasing the Prince and which would leave an everlasting impression for centuries to come. This Classic Dessert, later named after its inventor, Franz Sacher, came to be known as "Sacher-Torte" and is a sacred antique passed down from generation to generation in Vienna. But the Original Recipe is Hotel Sacher's best kept secret and protected with a trademark still. Oven Fresh's Sacher-Torte is made with two layers of spongy Chocolate Dacquoise in between which delectable Apricot Jam is spread and ultimately glazed with Belgian Chocolate Ganache making it a flavourful replica of Sacher's Invention ! Finally garnished with pure chocolate & cocoa powder, this Torte is ready to reach your doorstep in a jiffy ! Our Chef's take on this vintage cake will make your mouth melt with relief & leave you craving for more. This cake with a 99.9% Gold Varakh is just royalty.

fields.title: Desire 3 ( Contain Egg )
fields.description: A rich almond dacoise base beautifully holds the delicately prepared chocolate choux pastry. The crunchy elements are finished with three different mousse varieties & coated with pure cocoa butter. Talk less and feel the Desire. When an artist sits to paint, little does he know that he will make a masterpiece; when a potter moulds the clay he is wishing for a beautiful urn; and when a baker churns the batter, he nearly falls in love with his cake. And that is precisely what happened to creative Patissiers at Ovenfresh when Desire III happened to them. Love knew no bounds when the chefs at Ovenfresh decided to whip up a glorious and celebrated cake that was never created before. They say, love is blind and when chef gave birth to a cake with six different textures and 36 ingredients, he certainly proved it right. Just like the meticulous virtues of understanding, romance and compatibility are needed to keep a relationship alive; the chef's love story with Desire III demanded both time and attention. His dedication was evident in the pre planning that was equivalent to that of constructing and building. The intricate planning process ran longer than the actual time taken to make it. After trying six different recipes and trivial combinations, back and forth on the right pairings it was time for celebration. Taking cue from French Patisserie heritage, chefs at Ovenfresh danced in merriment when the Desire III finally saw the light of the day just in the first attempt. It was the first ever magnanimous creation that rightfully earned its reputation as Ovenfresh's signature cake. And there is no reason why this three-in-one dessert does not deserve the golden mantle. The combination of six unique textures and tastes also has a spectrum of appearances. Crunchy, gooey and soft, Desire III embodies the best of the baking world. A rich almond dacoise base beautifully holds the delicately prepared chocolate choux pastry. And the elaborateness just does not end there. The crunchy elements are then finished with three different mousse varieties and are coated with a deep red cover. Even the look of the cake found its inspiration in the classy architectures of history. The neoclassical appearance combines the old and new while the clean and smooth top gives it a contemporary touch. The rustic and archaic architecture of ancient empires stimulated. The complex flavours of the cake are so extravagant that recreating it is almost impossible. Recipes can be duplicated for once, but love for food is unique and not all can show the same. The only way to express your love and emotions for this cake is by committing to a relationship with Desire III. Several encounters and a gradual understanding are necessary to feel the Desire to its fullest potential. True to its name, this is certainly an object of Desire for every passionate cake lover. The passionate love affair between the patissiere and Desire is a romantic fantasy one can only dream of. And the best way to live this sinful and divine experience would be do delve into its heavenly goodness one bite at a time. A small message looks very elegant with this cake.
